author: aconway
msg: QPID-4136: HA sporadic failures in ha_tests
Caused by a test bug, default timeout was too short.
Fixed the test to set a high timeout and increased default timeout.

msg: Fixed a regression in Axis2 caused by the recent StAX(OM)Builder changes.

author: aconway
msg: QPID-4133: (Jason Dillaman) Non-responsive peer in federated link can result in entire cluster shutdown
Fix is to not start link processing until the connection is open.
